<div dir="ltr"><span id="docs-internal-guid-a406e7e9-bbdf-977c-fd21-8b3550946972"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Hey folks!</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">We just released another beta version of Ushahidi v3. </span></p><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:10pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">What’s in it?</span></h2><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">A sneak peek into some of the things to expect from this release:-</span></p><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">New features like:-</span></p></li><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap">Viewing Collections and Saved Searches.</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap">Adding posts to collections</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Configuring twitter data sources and pulling in messages based on hashtags/other search terms</span></p></li></ul><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Improvements such as</span></p></li><ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">An updated user profile editor</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">A cleaned up and fixed timeline view</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:circle;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;background-color:transparent"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Better authentication handling. </span><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap">Users are only redirected to login when necessary</span></p></li></ul><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:disc;font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap">AND SO MUCH MORE :)</span></p></li></ul><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Have a look at </span><a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/platform/releases/tag/v3.0.0-beta.21" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">our release notes</span></a><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> and </span><a href="http://wp.me/p4vfAA-4vQ" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">blog post announcement</span></a><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent"> for more details on changes in this release. </span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;background-color:transparent">Take it out for a spin on our </span><a href="http://demo.platform.ushahidi.com/" style="text-decoration:none"><span style="font-family:&#39;Proxima Nova&#39;;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wra